-=Map Information=-

fy_iceworld_hdr (v1.0) created by Wizman87

.BSP and .NAV files are included in the .RAR/ZIP file.

fy_iceworld_hdr.RAR/ZIP | 256KB / 276KB
      fy_iceworld_hdr.BSP | 524KB
      fy_iceworld_hdr.NAV | 68KB

Just so everyone knows, this is another remake of the original fy_iceworld for CS:S, except with the improvement and addition of HDR and snow! =D

And as a side note, just to make myself clear, I created this map from scratch - it was not copied/decompiled in any way, shape, or form.

Have fun and enjoy my version of fy_iceworld! ^^

I hope it is as popular as the first! =D

Greets! ^^



-=Instructions=-

Extract the files included inside the .RAR/ZIP file to your counter-strike source\cstrike\maps directory.



-=Contact E-mail & MSN=-

Have any questions or want to report a bug? Send or message me an E-mail or IM to:

Wizman87@yahoo.com



-=NOTES=-

Special thanks to the original designer and creator of fy_iceworld.
